This paper proposes a new architecture for Transformers that improves their ability to exploit the sequential nature of input data. As such, it is likely to be relevant to several sub-categories of computer science, including natural language processing (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE), and computer vision (cs.CV).
